      "content": "i'm just so frustrated with how much i have to deal with. if garlic is so dangerous because it affects the blood, wouldn't that actually be a good thing if i'm taking it specifically to act as my thinner? like, if i take a really high dose of garlic extract and keep up with the kale smoothies, wouldn't that basically just be a natural version of what the warfarin does? i just want a way to manage it without the chemicals.",
